{"synckey":1585453090,"updated":[{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"自由地享受时光，让我们感受到了时间的公平性，而时间的不可逆性，却时常会让我们焦虑和无奈。正因为时间的这种一去不复返的特性，让我们狂奔在追逐时间的路上。","range":"5663-5738","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_5663-5738","createTime":1585452990,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"如果你想在任何方面变得更好，你就必须爱上它的执行过程。你必须爱上成为想成为的那种人的过程，而非仅仅想要得到某个结果。","range":"4094-4152","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_4094-4152","createTime":1585452880,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"对过程的关注会使你不仅享受到好的结果，更能够让你持续专注于后续生活里那些重要的事情。","range":"3877-3919","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_3877-3919","createTime":1585452832,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"保持长期专注的第二件事是专注于过程，而不是完成某件事情","range":"3596-3623","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_3596-3623","createTime":1585452790,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"你要开始试着用客观的指标来衡量你做事情的结果，从而帮助自己始终专注于重要的事情，忽略那些无关紧要的事情","range":"3532-3583","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_3532-3583","createTime":1585452773,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"只有通过数字和清晰的跟踪，我们才能知道事情是变好了还是变坏了。","range":"3228-3259","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_3228-3259","createTime":1585452734,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"「衡量结果」可以让我们保持聚焦和专注力","range":"3187-3206","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_3187-3206","createTime":1585452711,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"如何延长注意力的时效并持续保持专注","range":"2968-2985","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_2968-2985","createTime":1585452653,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"无论如何，直到你达成前5名的目标之前，这些事情都不应该引起你的注意。”","range":"2738-2773","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_2738-2773","createTime":1585452617,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"将注意力集中在重要的事情上，而非不重要的事情","range":"2234-2256","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_2234-2256","createTime":1585452567,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"据研究，如果一个人每五分钟检查一次邮箱，那他平均需要花费64秒才能恢复执行上一个任务。","range":"2003-2046","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_2003-2046","createTime":1585452529,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"大多数人无法集中精力，往往是因为他们很难做抉择，不懂得设定事情的轻重缓急。","range":"1238-1275","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_1238-1275","createTime":1585452483,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"如何才能专注于那件更重要的事情而忽略哪些不重要的事情呢？","range":"1169-1197","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_1169-1197","createTime":1585452475,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"专注是高效的关键，因为拒绝做其他事情的同时，你才能让自己有精力去完成剩下来的那件事情。","range":"1114-1157","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_1114-1157","createTime":1585452463,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"「选择」是集中注意力的前提","range":"979-992","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_979-992","createTime":1585452448,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"只有当我们对一个选项说“是”，而对所有其他选项说“不”的时候，专注才会出现。","range":"939-977","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_939-977","createTime":1585452434,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"在一个时间段里，专注地去做好该做的事情。","range":"694-714","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_694-714","createTime":1585452413,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"时间管理的本质，不是管理时间，而是管理好我们的注意力。","range":"602-629","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_602-629","createTime":1585452399,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"我们可以通过有意识地管理注意力来达成目标，实现理想。","range":"321-347","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_321-347","createTime":1585452370,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","markText":"只有注意力是真正属于我们自己，并且能够为我们所自由支配。","range":"270-298","bookmarkId":"MP_WXS_3286632880_qze0uqcVqOGbuNchZSGq5Q_270-298","createTime":1585452365,"type":1},{"bookId":"MP_WXS_3286632880","